summary: GAMETECH RELEASING PU LEATHER EVA POUCH SW FOR SWITCH
title: GAMETECH RELEASING PU LEATHER EVA POUCH SW FOR SWITCH
body: GameTech’s next Switch accessory is the “PU Leather EVA Pouch SW,” which is what they’re saying are high-quality pouches for your Switch. The couch has a leather-like finish, and includes a carrying handle. These cases can hold a Switch with two Joy-Con attached, a pair of Joy-Con, two cables, cloth, earphones, and ten game cards. The color options include black, blue, and red. These cases will release in Japan on May 20th, 2019.

summary: 70-YEAR-OLD POKEMON GO SUPER-PLAYER GETS SPONSORSHIP DEAL WITH ASUS
title: 70-YEAR-OLD POKEMON GO SUPER-PLAYER GETS SPONSORSHIP DEAL WITH ASUS
body:
Remember the 70-year-old Taiwanese Pokemon GO player Chen San Yuan? The man who rides around on a bike with a phone rig that allows him to play 21 games of Pokemon GO at once? Mr. Chen just found himself a new gig thanks to his Pokemon GO fanaticism…brand ambassador for ASUS!

ASUS liked what Mr. Chen was doing so much that they brought him in to help promote the Zenfone Max Pro M2, one of their newest phones. They even had Mr. Chen’s bike rig outfitted with 21 of their Zenfone Max Pro M2 phones, so he can hop right back in to playing Pokemon GO!

title: BUSTAFELLOWS - 'SUPPLEMENTARY CAST' TRAILER
body: The east American town of New Seeg. Limbo Fitzgerald, who is well-known as a crooked lawyer, received an urgent defense request and made his way to the police station. There, he met a man who told him, “Without this meeting, destiny would have killed you, Limbo.” The man’s strange words confused Limbo. And then the man said, with an unnatural and woman-like tone, “‘Today’ is a rerun for me. I saw you die with my own eyes.”
